  "body": "Perhaps you can add support for shift-left in the SafeMath library:\r\n\r\n```\r\nfunction shl(uint256 x, uint8 y) internal pure returns (uint256) {\r\n    uint256 z = x << y;\r\n    assert((z >> y) == x);\r\n    return z;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n",
