    "body": "@wbt:\r\nYou seem to be forgetting the fact that computing the power of 2 by itself has a \"price tag\" attached to it.\r\n\r\nIf the exponent is known then you can use a constant value of course, but otherwise, the operation `x << y` would be replaced with `x * uint256(2) ** y`, which has a much higher \"price tag\" attached to it.",
